Corporate Banking RM - PT Bank ICBC Indonesia
Corporate Banking RM  -
Corporate Banking RM
Responsibilities
To implement business activities and credit operational management in Investment and Corporate Banking in order to achieve Asset target, fee based income target, expansion of target market, quality of service and business growth.To conduct loan acquisition and establish good relationships with prospective customers (the scope of works including but not limited to : to prepare credit proposal, monitor and manage the credit approval process, monitor and manage the loan agreement and disbursement)To manage the accounts that have been acquired in the current category and sound performance Requirements Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor's Degree, Master's Degree / Post Graduate Degree, Economics, Finance/Accountancy/Banking, Business Studies/Administration/Management, Marketing, Commerce or equivalent.At least 5 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.Placement : Head Office.Language : English and Mandarin.Full-Time position(s) available.
